{"tid":840680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"重磅！ 德媒爆料：C朗涉強姦案 仲要畀掩口費","createTime":"2018-09-29T03:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T10:59:45.000Z","uid":54373,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e82190030230401334a9d7891cc48568fedead","tid":840680,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"《德國之聲》引述德國《明鏡》周刊報道，效力祖雲達斯的葡萄牙球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）捲入性醜聞，他被指於2009年在美國拉斯維加斯一間酒店，強姦一名女子。不過《明鏡》指，C朗當時已否認指控，強調雙方都是合意性交。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，事主為34歲美國女子Kathryn Mayorga，事件發生於2009年6月12日，地點為拉斯維加斯的一間酒店。Mayorga指，當時效力皇家馬德里的C朗正在拉斯維加斯度假，他們一起參加派對，但之後更被對方強姦。事後雙方在內華達州達成庭外和解協議，C朗向Mayorga支付了375,000美元（約293萬港元)的掩口費。<br />\n<br />\nMayorga又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">C朗當時下跪道歉，強調自己是「99%的好人」，只是被「剩下的1%」拖累，最終做了錯事。</span>《明鏡》指C朗當時已否認指控，不過到目前為此，C朗本人都未有現身回應。"},{"pid":"09047dd53d8273248635943b8b903c8f56da7267","tid":840680,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"33c7d602a4d00b1370a1ab13dc90383e53655fe7","tid":840680,"uid":54373,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"1%壞人<br />\n1.82%入球率<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92c5b394685df15b1b09718fb7fd97a3873705b","tid":840680,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33c7d602a4d00b1370a1ab13dc90383e53655fe7","tid":840680,"uid":54373,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"1%壞人<br />\n1.82%入球率<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"